This is a "plugin" for the Video Disk Recorder (VDR).

Written by:                  Martin Schirrmacher <vdr.skinflatplus@schirrmacher.eu>

Project's homepage:          http://projects.vdr-developer.org/projects/plg-skinflatplus/


